      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Good, honest example that presents well overall and should make a very enjoyable driver. The body, paint, and trim show nicely from a normal distance, with the expected minor cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d want to see disclosed on a car that has been used and cared for rather than over-restored. The interior is tidy and usable, showing some wear consistent with age, but overall it remains a pleasant place to spend time. Mechanically, expect a solid driver that can be enjoyed as-is, not a perfect show car, but a well-sorted car suitable for regular use, local events, and weekend drives.",
      "price": 31900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition example that appears to be a usable driver, but not a fully sorted or especially fresh car. It shows its age with visible cosmetic wear, imperfections in the finish and trim, and an overall presentation that is decent from a distance but clearly not restored. The interior is serviceable and complete, though expect wear consistent with age and use. Best suited for someone who wants an affordable driver to improve over time, rather than a turn-key show car.",
      "price": 17900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a practical buyer who values affordability over perfection, but it remains a solid opportunity for local driving, a starter vehicle, or a project. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive wheels with straightforward value, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an affordable way into a set of wheels and would suit someone after a cheap runabout, first project, or handy spare car. Friendly, straightforward sale and priced to make sense for what it is.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast potential. The powertrain fires up, pulls through the revs, and the chassis still feels fundamentally usable, making this a strong candidate for someone who wants an affordable platform to sort and improve. It shows age and needs cosmetic/mechanical attention, but the core package is there: a complete car with character, good parts value, and plenty of upside for a hands-on owner. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    }
